Revision history for Perl module Mojolicious-Plugin-Multiplex

1.0 2018-11-06
  - Provide an ECMAScript module
  - The old-school javascript library is now built from it using webpack

0.06 2018-09-08
  - Refactor the javascript to handle unsubscriptions more cleanly

0.05 2017-11-21
  - Add non-standard jsonmessage event to WebSocketMultiplexChannel

0.04 2017-11-21
  - Rename the Channel class WebSocketMultiplexChannel for consistency
  - Replace DumbEventTarget with EventTarget as base class for WebSocketMultiplexChannel

0.03 2017-11-13
  - Use File::Share to move javascript files to share directory
  - Add url parameter to multiplex js object
  - Allow changing url between reconnects in javascript

0.02 2016-08-23
  - Client caches channel objects rather than overwriting them
  - Rename error method to send_error

0.01 2016-08-22
  - Initial release

